title: Pickles & Dosa Lite
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Take-out, Catering, Pakistani, Indo-Chinese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Was originally veg but added s section of meat dishes to its menu. Sit-down Indian restaurant offering numerous varieties of dosa in addition to Indo-Chinese food and other Indian food like thali, uthappam (pancakes), Bombay chawpatti chat (snacks). Weekend breakfast specials. Dairy/ghee is used in the food. Previously located in a different location on South St.
